      "text": [
        " قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) الرَّجُلُ يَأْتِي ذَاتَ مَحْرَمٍ قَالَ يُضْرَبُ ضَرْبَةً بِالسَّيْفِ .    "
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from his father, from Ibn Bukeyr, from a man who said, ",
          "‘I said to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, ‘The man comes to his <span class=\"iTxt\">Mahram</span>’. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He would be struck with one strike of the sword’."
        ]
      }
